  <brief_title>Automated Ventilator Controlled Weaning vs Daily Spontaneous Breathing Trial in Difficult to Wean ICU Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Automated Ventilator Controlled Weaning to Daily Spontaneous Breathing Trial Weaning Protocol in ICU Patients Following Prolonged Mechanical Ventilation.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>University of California, San Francisco</agency>
