  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will compare Drager Smart Care (SC), a commercially available automated ventilator
      controlled weaning mode to the current daily spontaneous breathing trial (SBT) weaning
      protocol. The study is designed to determine if automated ventilator controlled weaning can
      reduce total duration of intubation following mechanical ventilation in ICU patients
      requiring prolonged mechanical ventilation (&gt;72 hours).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
